    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Configurando o ID da sua pasta de backups nos nodes do Google Drive\n\nVa ate sua pasta de backups no Drive e copie o **`id da pasta`** \n\n![Image](https://i.imgur.com/PXtVwYl.png)\n\nO id vai estar logo apﾃｳs a palavra **`folders`**\n\n```\nfolders/id-da-sua-pasta\n```\n\nCopie esse id e cole no campo '**`Filter`**' do node **getFolder**\n![Image](https://i.imgur.com/Jz1K2iG.png)\n\nCole o id tambem no campo '**`Parent Folder`**' do node **createFolder**\n![Image](https://i.imgur.com/70QqRbV.png)\n",
